"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-max-whitlock-retirement-paris-olympics-2024-b1150506.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Max Whitlockwill retire following theParis Olympics, he announced on Wednesday morning.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whitlock is a three-time Olympic champion and boasts six medals spanning three Games dating back to London 2012.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.810005690235147e-17, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999682306685, \"rank\": 3.0930739123560084e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he has set his sights on a golden Games farewell in the French capital this summer on the pommel horse, his No1 apparatus.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8556446330214219, \"rank\": 0.1622716395378437, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The decision now feels right,\\\" Whitlock told BBC Breakfast.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.810005690235147e-17, \"text\": \"Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}, {\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Breakfast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BBC Breakfast\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Breakfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Breakfast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Going for my final Olympic Games, it feels very, very strange talking about it, and it's almost hard to articulate what it's like.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really nice mindset to be in, to think I will just give it all I have got.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever since Rio where I was at my peak age, I think I have had questions thrown at me about when am I retiring.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have wanted to prove people wrong a lot of the way through my journey and I have always had the mindset of trying to do this for as long as I possibly can.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now, I have given myself the opportunity for Willow [his daughter] to come and watch an Olympic Games because she could not in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9853972999041324, \"rank\": 0.0147884122408888, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's such a good feeling for me.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I am in areas competing, Willow waits for it to go quiet and she calls for me, and we do this double thumbs-up.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I'd love to do that in the Paris Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9651119284465218, \"rank\": 0.033170670